OL,7,FThe mother died at the scene. The two
OL,8,Fgirls were injured.
OL,10,FAshley Towning, who was almost four
OL,11,Ftimes over the legal limit and under
OL,12,Fthe influence of drugs, then fled the
OL,13,Fscene. Police say it was also highly
OL,14,Flikely that he was using his phone
OL,15,Fwhen the collision happened.
