OL,7,FWitnesses said they saw and heard
OL,8,FTowning's car accelerating loudly
OL,9,Fbefore it hit the kerb and mounted the
OL,10,Fpavement, and that the car looked to
OL,11,Fbe out of control. They said the
OL,12,Fdriver did not make any attempt to
OL,13,Fsteer back into the road.
OL,15,FHis car stopped as it hit a streetlamp
OL,16,Fwhich then toppled over. He then got
OL,17,Fout of the car and fled, leaving
OL,18,Fbehind his driving licence and two
OL,19,Fbottles of vodka; one was empty.
