OL,7,FHe was found by officers 11 minutes
OL,8,Flater hiding under his dining room
OL,9,Ftable.
OL,11,FA breath test showed he was almost
OL,12,Ffour times over the legal drink drive
OL,13,Flimit and had cocaine, benzoylecgonine
OL,14,Fand cannabis in his system.
OL,16,FTowning, 30, of Winchester Road,
OL,17,FGrantham, pleaded guilty to causing
OL,18,Fdeath by dangerous driving, failing to
OL,19,Fstop and drink-driving.
